Description: 13 fragments of Coptic codex pages. Twelve frames (EA 76565-76) are stored together in an archival box.
Curator's comments: EA 76415 may belong to the same group.
Previously unregistered material stored in Papyrus Store. The frame labelled '1847-1848 No. 276 3161 Hartwell Mus. No 6'.
Acquisition notes: 'Gift of papyri from Hartwell House by Messrs Rutter and Marchant.'
